Preheat the oven to 400째F (200째C).
Start by making the crust. Crack eggs into a medium-sized bowl and add shredded cheese. 
Give it a good stir till the cheese is covered by the eggs
Use a spatula to spread the cheese and egg batter on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper as a large rectangular pizza.
Bake in the oven for 15 minutes
Remove and let cool for a minute or two.
Increase the oven temperature to 450째F (225째C).
Spread tomato sauce on the crust and sprinkle oregano on top
Top with cheese and place the pepperoni and olives on top.
Bake for another 5-10 minutes
Serve with a fresh salad on the side.
